Sample site: 
    roi.ru

Main features:
. search proposals
. tags for proposals
. view on map
. vote for proposal
. comment on pages
. receive notifications by email
    
User roles:
. admin
. regular user (who applies proposals)

Architecture:
- web app
- server side platform:  Spring 3 with Hibernate with JPA2
- persistence: MySQL 
- client: jQuery with Bootstrap
- infrastructure tools: git, maven, sts, junit, log4j